title: Poorly Done
review: Michael Jai White is a decent actor with incredible martial arts skills. Please get him a script for a good movie!!!!!!!

title: Let's throw all the cliches and see which ones stick
review: Poorly written, poorly directed, terrible acting by almost everyone and the most outrageous collection of cliches I have come across in quite a while. Sadly, it doesn't fall in the "it's so bad it's good" category. It's just bad.

title: A waste of good talent
review: The first movie by Jai White that I find boring to the grave. A waste of Jai White's time.
